METEO FVG Light è la versione più "leggera" dell'App "METEO FVG", dedicata ai dispositivi non particolarmente veloci o non compatibili con iOS7 (iPhone3G/3GS).
Con METEO FVG Light puoi, con estrema facilità, accedere:
- alle previsioni fino a 3 gg. pubblicate dall'Osservatorio Meteorologico Regionale;
- alla mappa Radar VMI;
- alla mappa satellitare;
- alle principali webcam installate sul territorio regionale.

TableTop Soccer is a tactical, turn-based, online multiplayer/single player game. With a heavy focus on strategy & tactics, play solo games, challenge friends, or players all over the world. Play live games or play resumable games over a few days to perfect your plan. Earn experience points scoring goals & winning games to level up your players, unlock abilities and customize your team to try to take the top spot on the Leaderboards.

You'll need to think fast and plan ahead to anticipate your opponent, react quickly and not succumb to pressure to crush your opponents' dreams and bring your team to victory.

Game Features:
*Compete online with players all over the world in live games;

*Challenge Friends to play online games;

*Play quick Live games, or play Resumable games over a few days – getting Notifications whenever it's your turn;

*Practice your technique against the AI Team “Evil Machines”;

*Simultaneous Turns - In live games, both players take their turn at the same time - make your moves before the timer runs out! 

*Earn points by winning games and scoring goals to upgrade the skills & abilities of your players to make the perfect team that matches your play style;

*Watch Replays of full games - your own games and those of other players, to learn new tricks and tips; 

*Climb the Leaderboards and level up your team from Novice to Master; 

*True Cross-Platform Multiplayer - All platforms play on the same servers;

*Get Mobile notifications when any Resumable game is ready for you to jump in;

**Requires an internet connection to play;

Orbita AI is a unique puzzle game where you solve tasks without ever touching the screen! Only using your smartphone capabilities. 

Test flexibility and quickness of your mind by shaking, spinning, turning and moving your smartphone!

There is no one who can describe Orbita AI better than the players themselves:
— “A one of a kind and the most addictive puzzle I’ve seen of late.” 
— “The kind of game you love and hate at the same time.”
— “I never knew what my phone was capable of until I completed all the levels.”

What can Orbita AI offer you?
• 47 exciting levels (we are constantly adding new ones);
• Eye-catching minimalistic design;
• Every level brings something new to the table;
• A lot of hidden secret levels to unlock;
• Witty tips in case if you’re stuck;
• A communicative and sarcastic AI.

Enjoy the game, but be careful. It’s really easy to lose track of time in it!

Impara l'italiano, metti alla prova le tue competenze e gioca con più di 180 parole, immagini e suoni.

"ABC for Kids" è un’applicazione ‘all-in-one’ per i bambini dagli 1 ai 7 anni. L'applicazione aiuta i bambini ad arricchire il proprio vocabolario e a sviluppare la loro percezione degli oggetti e delle creature viventi. 

I bambini potranno imparare in modo interattivo tutto su: 
- Alfabeto; 
- Numeri; 
- Animali: Animali domestici, animali selvatici, animali acquatici, uccelli, insetti; 
- Colori; 
- Forme; 
- Verdure; 
- Frutta; 
- Mezzi di trasporto; 
- Strumenti musicali; 
- Fiori; 
- Mestieri; 
- Attrezzi; 
- Sport; 
- Dolci; 
- Oggetti. 

Le immagini sono accompagnate dalla pronuncia in lingua italiana e da altri suoni specifici.

Gli interventi vocali (voce femminile) sono registrati in uno studio di registrazione professionale. 

L'App ha tre sezioni:

1.Impara- naviga attraverso le varie sezioni educative o lascia che vengano riprodotte automaticamente. I bambini possono toccare l’immagine per ascoltare il suono corrispondente. 

2. Testa – metti alla prova le tue competenze in ogni categoria 

Scegli tra quattro immagini per trovare quella corretta. 

3. Gioca - metti alla prova le tue competenze in più categorie. 
Scegli tra un insieme di 16 categorie trova di volta in volta la voce corretta. 

Informazioni personalizzate per il bisogno di scoperta dei bambini, insieme a nuovi test e giochi, verranno aggiunti periodicamente alla lista degli strumenti interattivi. 

È possibile utilizzare l'applicazione su tutti i dispositivi: iPhone, iPad o iPod touch (è richiesta la versione iOS 5.0 minimo). 

L’Audio non funziona? 
Alza il volume e controlla che il dispositivo non sia impostato su Muto. Puoi trovare i pulsanti Mute e quelli del volume sul lato del dispositivo.

Classics always works its magic – play Magic Chess 3D on your device!
Take part in the intellectual duel of wizards;
Lead your magic chess army to the victory;
Use various strategies to win the game;
Win this fascinating magic challenge!

Magic Chess 3D is far from being a boring chess game. It transforms your usual game of chess into a breath-taking clash of two magic armies. Outwit AI and lead your army to the victory!

- Classic rules, classy appearance;
- Epic collision of two eternal enemies;
- Advanced chess AI as a virtual rival;
- Test different grand master combinations.

Formation lap is almost over, as you push gently on the throttle and brutally steer one last time from left to right, trying to mantain a high temperature on your wheels. You know it's the key to get through the first corner as fast as you can. Probably it will allow you to make a good start and overtake the two cars in front of you. They already reached their starting spots.
It's time to lift up gas pedal and focus on that yellow line on your grid spot. While gently applying pressure on the brake pedal, you try to gain every millimeter the regulation permits, and perfectly line up your front wing with the white line defining your starting position. 
Now you are pushing the paddles on the bottom part of your steering wheel, disengaging the clutch. Shift from 2nd to 1st gear. The car is still.
First red light of the traffic light turns on. You did this already, you know how to do it. Your right foot pushes gently gas pedal.
Second red light is on, rpm hits the limiter.
Third red light is on. The engine now howles loud, while you try to find the right rpms for a perfect start.
Four red light is on. The heat distortion waves of the cars in front of you suggest all drivers are ready for the fight.
Fifth red light is on. A fast glance to the steering wheel display. Everything is ok.
Lights are out... 

*Game Features*
-20 customizable cars;
-15 REAL circuits from all over the world;
-Exciting AI for great challenges!
-5 different tyres type for different handling;
-Pit stop: decide your strategy and take an advantage on rivals;
-Real Time Damages;
-Team Radio;
-Global leaderboards;
- ...And a lot more!

Like to shoot pool? Come on to download Cool Billiards Game - Pocket Pool Pro for FREE right now!

☆☆☆☆☆ How to play ☆☆☆☆☆
- VERSUS MODE
Play against the computer AI with standard 8 ball rules or 9 ball rules. Touch the screen to adjust the direction or press buttons to adjust cue angle slightly, drag down the power-up in the RIGHT to shoot. Touch and hold at any point to move the cue-ball and tap to confirm for Free-ball.

- CHALLENGE MODE
You need to pocket all the balls on the table within the given number of cues. There is no time limit for this mode, but watch out there may have various traps and you have only limited number of cues.

☆☆☆☆☆ Highlighted Features ☆☆☆☆☆  
- Realistic 3D ball and great physical experience;
- Various game modes, 8 Ball Pool, 9 Ball Pool and up to 150 levels arcade mode;
- Player vs Computer AI (AI with 3 levels);
- Various tables;
- Bright and vibrant graphics & effects.

